152
00:14:49,794 --> 00:14:52,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even though you brought me there</b></font>

153
00:14:52,804 --> 00:14:56,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so that I could be with Kazumi...</b></font>

154
00:14:56,804 --> 00:15:00,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I just couldn't tell her how I felt.</b></font>

155
00:15:04,744 --> 00:15:08,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been thinking about her
constantly since yesterday.</b></font>

156
00:15:08,584 --> 00:15:13,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Falling in love with her
made me realize something.</b></font>

157
00:15:13,484 --> 00:15:17,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Loving someone is really a painful thing.</b></font>

158
00:15:30,334 --> 00:15:34,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Loving someone is serious business.</b></font>

159
00:15:34,174 --> 00:15:38,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When it doesn't work out,
your chest aches so much.</b></font>

160
00:15:38,944 --> 00:15:41,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Laugh at me if you want.</b></font>

161
00:15:41,584 --> 00:15:44,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why would I laugh?</b></font>

162
00:15:44,284 --> 00:15:46,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know the feeling?</b></font>

163
00:15:46,084 --> 00:15:47,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

164
00:15:54,834 --> 00:15:57,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

165
00:16:22,224 --> 00:16:25,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--You're back late.
--Yeah.</b></font>

166
00:16:25,264 --> 00:16:28,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You only have an hour until your deliveries.</b></font>

167
00:16:28,894 --> 00:16:30,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know.</b></font>

168
00:16:30,234 --> 00:16:33,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wake me up when it's time.</b></font>

169
00:16:33,064 --> 00:16:34,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure.</b></font>

170
00:16:37,604 --> 00:16:41,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I never knew that our car was that good.</b></font>

171
00:16:43,714 --> 00:16:45,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Dad?</b></font>

172
00:16:45,544 --> 00:16:48,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe you can teach me
about engines and stuff</b></font>

173
00:16:48,614 --> 00:16:51,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>when you have time.</b></font>

174
00:16:51,554 --> 00:16:55,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened all of a sudden?</b></font>

175
00:16:55,394 --> 00:16:59,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I realized which essential
element I was lacking.</b></font>

176
00:17:23,054 --> 00:17:26,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, Itsuki is acting weird.</b></font>

177
00:17:29,394 --> 00:17:33,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll find out eventually
anyway, so I'll tell you.</b></font>

178
00:17:36,264 --> 00:17:40,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. That's really unfortunate.</b></font>

179
00:17:40,564 --> 00:17:42,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought they'd make it.</b></font>

180
00:17:42,734 --> 00:17:46,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's back to being the "Lonely Driver."</b></font>

181
00:17:48,774 --> 00:17:50,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki?</b></font>

182
00:17:51,384 --> 00:17:52,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

183
00:17:57,384 --> 00:17:58,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi!</b></font>

184
00:17:58,924 --> 00:18:00,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

185
00:18:00,624 --> 00:18:03,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Didn't you go back to Saitama?</b></font>

186
00:18:03,654 --> 00:18:05,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was all so sudden.</b></font>

187
00:18:05,664 --> 00:18:08,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I came back to get my stuff.</b></font>

188
00:18:08,494 --> 00:18:10,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, yeah?</b></font>

189
00:18:10,134 --> 00:18:13,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that's not all I left here.</b></font>

190
00:18:13,134 --> 00:18:14,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We left in a hurry,</b></font>

191
00:18:14,834 --> 00:18:18,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I couldn't say goodbye to you properly.</b></font>

192
00:18:20,044 --> 00:18:21,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi?</b></font>

193
00:18:21,544 --> 00:18:25,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you free now? Just for an hour?</b></font>

194
00:18:25,184 --> 00:18:27,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have some time.</b></font>

195
00:18:32,024 --> 00:18:34,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He had to leave early...</b></font>

196
00:18:34,084 --> 00:18:36,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...for personal reasons.</b></font>

197
00:18:36,254 --> 00:18:37,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Again?</b></font>

198
00:18:37,924 --> 00:18:40,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bittersweet youth...</b></font>

199
00:18:40,264 --> 00:18:44,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's the most important
thing to him right now.</b></font>

200
00:18:44,704 --> 00:18:46,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That reminds me.</b></font>

201
00:18:46,704 --> 00:18:49,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, I heard that your girlfriend</b></font>

202
00:18:49,734 --> 00:18:52,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--started a part-time job.
--What?</b></font>

203
00:18:52,544 --> 00:18:55,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How are things with you two?</b></font>

204
00:18:58,544 --> 00:19:00,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mogi got a job...?</i></b></font>

205
00:19:08,994 --> 00:19:11,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Autumn is almost over.</b></font>

206
00:19:12,994 --> 00:19:17,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll never forget this autumn in Akina.</b></font>

207
00:19:17,494 --> 00:19:21,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll think of it every time
the leaves change colors.</b></font>

208
00:19:21,904 --> 00:19:25,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll never forget the people I met in Gunma...</b></font>

209
00:19:25,044 --> 00:19:29,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...especially this outspoken
but compassionate boy</b></font>

210
00:19:29,344 --> 00:19:34,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>who encouraged me to live.</b></font>

211
00:19:34,484 --> 00:19:36,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's a year younger than I am,</b></font>

212
00:19:36,854 --> 00:19:41,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and is like the little brother I never had.</b></font>

213
00:19:41,924 --> 00:19:44,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't forget him.</b></font>

214
00:20:05,714 --> 00:20:08,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

215
00:20:08,384 --> 00:20:12,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome! For here or to go?</b></font>

216
00:20:11,184 --> 00:20:16,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>Whenever I turned around</i></b></font>

217
00:20:12,584 --> 00:20:16,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Shibusawa Station"</b></font>

218
00:20:16,094 --> 00:20:21,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>There was always that</i></b></font>

219
00:20:16,094 --> 00:20:21,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>unchanging smile of yours</i></b></font>

220
00:20:21,364 --> 00:20:26,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>It was there on days when</i></b></font>

221
00:20:21,364 --> 00:20:26,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>I was too tired to go on</i></b></font>

222
00:20:26,034 --> 00:20:34,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>And even on days with a little happiness in them</i></b></font>

223
00:20:34,814 --> 00:20:43,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>My hands aren't enough</i></b></font>

224
00:20:43,414 --> 00:20:50,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>To hold on to all the love you gave me</i></b></font>

225
00:20:44,114 --> 00:20:47,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Goodbye, Kazumi.</i></b></font>

226
00:20:51,764 --> 00:20:54,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I couldn't tell you this...</i></b></font>

227
00:20:52,494 --> 00:20:59,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>The warm wind</i></b></font>

228
00:20:54,424 --> 00:20:56,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...but I loved you.</i></b></font>

229
00:20:59,734 --> 00:21:07,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>Comes back quietly and tenderly</i></b></font>

230
00:21:07,344 --> 00:21:15,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>It blows through with a radiant light</i></b></font>

231
00:21:15,354 --> 00:21:24,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>Just like it did that day</i></b></font>

232
00:21:39,444 --> 00:21:43,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother... have you formed
the All Gunma Team yet?</b></font>

233
00:21:42,374 --> 00:21:47,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>The grave sin of betrayal</i></b></font>

234
00:21:43,544 --> 00:21:45,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've picked the candidates.</b></font>

235
00:21:47,444 --> 00:21:52,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>The strength of believing in each other</i></b></font>

236
00:21:48,284 --> 00:21:51,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now it's up to them to join the team.</b></font>

237
00:21:52,584 --> 00:21:57,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>The countless days and nights</i></b></font>

238
00:21:54,794 --> 00:21:57,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't keep losing like this!</i></b></font>

239
00:21:57,424 --> 00:22:06,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}<i>Let's tuck them away in our hearts</i></b></font>

240
00:21:57,794 --> 00:22:00,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll get my revenge on the Emperors...</i></b></font>

241
00:22:00,094 --> 00:22:02,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...and Akina's Eight-Six!</i></b></font>

242
00:22:12,444 --> 00:22:21,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>On the road of meetings and partings</i></b></font>

243
00:22:21,354 --> 00:22:31,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We keep on walking while our hearts get hurt</i></b></font>

244
00:22:33,724 --> 00:22:41,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are still waving to me from the radiant light</i></b></font>

245
00:22:41,604 --> 00:22:51,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just like you did that day</i></b></font>

246
00:22:54,284 --> 00:22:59,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are my everlasting memory</i></b></font>

